<br />
<h2>Create a new group</h2>
<p>To create a new group, click on the button "Create New Group" and fill out the required information.</p>
<div  class="hlp_figures"><img src="../modules/{$node_id}/images/hlp_grouplist_new.png" border="0" />
<p>Figure 2</p></div>
<br />
<p>To assign or modify permissions to a group go to the module "Group Permissions".</p>
